DOCUMENT_ID_DESC: The ID of the selected document request
DOCUMENTS_REGARDING_DESC: Lookup to the entity which is associated with the document
REGARDING_NAME_DESC: A required field indicating the “Regarding“ entity’s name
REGARDING_CONTEXT_DESC: The field showing how the “Regarding“ entity is connected to the parent entity
REGARDING_ROLE_DESC: The field indicates the role of the “Regarding“ entity within the parent entity
REGARDING_IS_PRIMARY_DESC: An attribute that indicates if the “Regarding“ entity is the primary entity within the parent entity
CONTEXT_ID_DESC: The ID of the parent entity which the document is requested for
BUSINESS_SCENARIO_DESC: The Business scenario. It is used in the UI to filter the available document type values once requesting a new document (e.g 104800001)
SHOW_DESCRIPTION_DESC: Show description. It is a text field to add brief description to document request
SHOW_DESCRIPTION_ENABLE_DESC: Enable add brief description to document request
SHOW_DESCRIPTION_DISABLE_DESC: Disable add brief description to document request
NEW_DOCUMENT_FORM_DESC: The ID of the quick create form to use when creating a document request
PIPELINE_RUNNING_MESSAGE: We need a few moments to analyze the document
PIPELINE_RUNNING_DESC: Try refreshing your browser, or wait a few moments.
PIPELINE_FAILURE_MESSAGE: System failed to analyze the document
PIPELINE_FAILURE_DESC: Try refreshing your browser, or wait a few moments.
